I really don't understand how you can fool me like that . Kissing me, saying you love me, holding me blah blah . And yesterday you fucking said you loved me again, and what .. Like .. A few hours later you write me a fucking SMS saying that you don't love me at all . Wtf ?! Are you that much of a coward ?! Can't you stand up to me and tell me to my face, that you've lost your feelings for me ? 

It's not that you don't have eny feelings for me, that makes me pissed, 'cause well . You can't control that . But you hide behind your fucking phone ! You can't look me in the eyes and tell me the truth, you fucktard !

You don't do that shit to me . You're going down mister !

Why is it, that you think you can have me as yours, when I'm free as a bird ? I'm not yours . Not anybody's . NOT your girl . I'm my own lady, and I can screw whoever the fuck I want ! And just because I slept with your best friend, doesen't give you the right to call me a whore ! You can call me a bitch, but you can NEVER call me a whore ! I didn't know you had feelings for me, and I kinda have a crush on your friend . And yes ! I slept with him . And it was good ! Better than anything YOU could ever give me, you twat ! So leave me the fuck alone, and let ME control MY sexlife, stupid ! And if you ever come near me . Oh, yes .. There will be some people who is going to get soooo pissed at you . So don't m'kay ?

OH MY GOD, I'M BORED !

oooh, today I'm going to the Roskilde festival .. Tomorrow also . .... AND YOU'RE NOT ! Haha .

I'm going to see my friends, and get wasted ! I'm going to dance around to good music, I'm going to have such an awesome time !!

Muhaha .

And today there was nothing .. as usual . I finally took my last exam and now I'm finished .. The last year at school has been awful .. The only thing I got out of it was a trip to Kentucky, which was something I'll never forget . I wish it could have been somewehere else, than Kentucky, but I got to know some very nice people . 

But like I said, the rest of the year has been a total waste of time .. 
And I hate living in this place sometimes ! The people around here are assholes ! I can stand the shit-talking and stuff . The name calling .. I don't care . But when they are grabbing yor ass and pulling down your shirt, while they're screaming that you got big tits, you get pissed .. Or in my case, I get furious ! 

Well, I tend to get very angry about nothing, and my friend don't even dare to try and say something to me . And maybe that's wise, 'cause I will go completely insane ! ..

So now I got some medication for that anger .. And it makes me sooooo sleepy .. Hope it helps me .

Fuck this .

I had a day off today, so i finally got some sleep . I hung out with Amalie a little bit a few hours ago, so that was nice . I am still a little bit tired and I have this horrible headache . Nothing new . Hope it goes away when I go to bed . 

Tomorrow, I'm going to see Amalie again and Mille . I'm looking foreward to it, and it feels nice, 'cause it's been a while since, I've been looking foreward to something . Yeah .

I miss Line very much . Going to see her this sunday .

So, now I'll just continue eating candy and driking Ribena .
GOD, I really need to get laid .

Sometimes I think I just can't be alone . I won't be alone . And sometimes I think I'm just better off alone . I feel like I'm hard to be around do to my terrible moodswings ....

I feel drained ... Forgotten ....



And I feel like crying, but I'm too fucking stubborn to do so .
Amalie took some photos of me last saturday . Anastasija edited two of them, and . here the edited are .

Right now I feel like punching someone so fucking hard in the face, that their nose will end up at the side of their head !

I was sitting down in a hallway, to get some peace and quiet, and then out of the blue, some girl gets all hysterical, and she's screaming non-stop that, she want to go home to her mom . At first, I was putting up with her screaming and people running around, slamming the doors and make so much noise, but then I just had it . Some woman asks me, if I'm feeling okay . What do you think, huh ? And yeah, like I said, I was getting pissed, so I told this woman that if they didn't get that bitch to shut up, I would choke her . ... And she left . Two seconds later i left the place . 

So in a few minuttes, I'm going to visit Anita . i love her .

The Psyclon nine koncert last saturday was AWESOME ! I was up front, dancing and singing with my best friend Amalie . Well, I had a blackout in the middle of everything, and I don't know why . Some friends had to drag me outside and get some water in me, and some icecubes . Drama, drama, drama . I'm so sorry guys . I didn't mean to worry you :(

But yeah, when I came to myself again, I pushed almost everyone aside to get up front again . hehe . Blackouts cannot stop me . muhaha .

After the concert, Psyclon Nine came out and talked to the audience . Yaaaaay ! They were soooo sweet . All of them . I had the best time . Thanks to Psyclon Nine, for giving such a great concert, and thanks to my friends for . yeah . beeing my friends and beeing there for me . Love you guys <3


Today . Problems . Oh dear .

Friday, I went to a birthday . It was nice, 'cause it was with some of my mom's family . And I havent' seen them since I was 11 years old . And even younger . I had a really good time .

Saturday, I went to Copenhagen with Damian <3 . It was nice to see him ^^ . And after that, I went to visit Anastasija . And I had a good time there too . Thanks for a great day ^^'

Today, I am just tired . Happy, but tired . and my stomach hurts a little bit . I've been doing absolutley nothing today . Nice .

Uh, I'm looking foreward to saturday . I'm going to a Psyclon Nine concert . One of my favorite bands . And I'm going with Amalie and Damian  ^^

So, yesterday I went to this market .. I should have been there with my mom, but she got sick, so my friend Line came with me .  It was a lot of fun . We were dancing and singing of course ^^

Today, Nicole came to visit me, and that was nice, 'cause I haven't seen her in a very loooong time .

She left a few hours ago, and I'm tired .. My stomach still hurts .. But it's the same, so the good thing is, that it's not getting any worse . I hope it's gone tomorrow . Well, I've talked to Damian about visiting him on thursday . And I'm also going to see him in cph on tuesday . I'm looking really foreward to see him . I miss him so much ..

I think i might go to bed early ..

Yesterday I was going to visit my boyfriend, but he was not feeling good, so I went out with some friends, that evening . I hope that Damian is feeling better soon <3

Today I'm a little tired . I have a stomach ache, but it's getting better . So that's good . 

I'm going to a marked here in Roskilde with my mom later . Just to see what kind of things they have out there . And to listen to a danish band called Shu-bi-dua . I'm looking foreward to it (:

So right now I am petting my dragon on his head ^^ . He loves the attention :P. And he just ate a bunch of worms, so he is very happy . haha .
